{
  "stem": "21004.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The head the rabbi and the other rabbi, everybody is just hiding or disappeared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody even knows.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this we-- so I was taking a plain--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A plain religious man, so he gave us-- he gave us the Jewish marriage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was taken away to the hard labor camp, I was married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now-- oh, you're going to the hard labor camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was talking about--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the hard work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was doing the hard work till 1940, till 1940, till April, 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, 1942, they took-- they took me to the hard labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When-- I was in touch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in touch when I was in the hard labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But how they take me to the hard labor camp-- well, they took us, I don't know, close to 1,000 people-- young men, older men-- not too older men-- young boys, even kids, like 11, 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took us to the city hall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the city hall, it was there, all regiment of Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was really Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they let us sit all around, all around, double, triple, just to sit around with our hands in the back and start irrigating the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they brought up shovels to build, to dig a hole in the middle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we start digging a hole very deep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took one Jew from another city, from-- he was from [INAUDIBLE], a city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They throw him in the grave, in the place, in the ditch, throw him deep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they say, throw some mud on him, everybody with shovels to throw mud on him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Later, they say stop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Everybody has to go in the containers, little containers, cups.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They open up the septic tanks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They open up.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
